io.amelia.data

Interface ValueTypesTrait<ExceptionClass extends ApplicationException.Error>


  • public interface ValueTypesTrait<ExceptionClass extends ApplicationException.Error>
    Provides common methods for converting an unknown value to (and from) Object using the Java 8 Optional feature.

    These types include: Boolean Color Double Enum Integer Long String File List Class
